<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>百度云网盘 on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E4%BA%91%E7%BD%91%E7%9B%98/</link><description>Recent content in 百度云网盘 on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2024 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Sat, 24 Sep 2016 12:52:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%99%BE%E5%BA%A6%E4%BA%91%E7%BD%91%E7%9B%98/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>百度云网盘自定义提取码</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/baidu-cloud-network-backup-custom-extracted-code/</link><pubDate>Sat, 24 Sep 2016 12:52:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/baidu-cloud-network-backup-custom-extracted-code/</guid><description>这篇文章介绍了如何在百度云网盘中使用自定义提取码。在浏览器打开百度云盘后，选中需要分享的文件并点击分享按钮。现在打开开发者工具的控制台，将提供的代码粘贴到控制台中并按回车。然后点击创建私密链接，并在弹出的输入框中输入自定义的密码即可。需要注意的是，自定义密码只能由4个字符组成，可以是字母、数字或一个汉字加上一个字母或数字。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/baidu-cloud-network-backup-custom-extracted-code/featured.png"/></item><item><title>百度云网盘提速</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/baiduyun/</link><pubDate>Mon, 12 Sep 2016 14:09:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/baiduyun/</guid><description>这篇文章介绍了如何提速百度云网盘下载的方法。作者提到，百度云网盘对非会员有很多限制，所以即使有很大空间也不能快速下载。作者列举了几种方法：一是开通会员，二是使用破解版或破解补丁，三是在浏览器上安装BaiduExporter插件，导出为aria2链接下载，四是安装百度网盘直接下载助手。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/baiduyun/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>